high_descs: turn right to face gold bin
pick up apple from gold bin
turn around, go to microwave above sink to the right
open microwave, place apple on left side of plate in microwave, microwave apple, take apple out of microwave, close microwave
look down to sink below microwave
place apple in sink on the right
Turn left and go towards the garbage bin on the floor next to the counter
Take the apple out of the garbage bin
Turn around and go towards the oven, then turn right and go to the sink
Cook the apple in the microwave above the sink then take the apple out of the microwave
Turn left then turn right to face the sinks
Put the apple in the larger sink on the right
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple into a sink

high_descs: Turn left and look down to face the trash can on the floor.
Pick up the apple in the trash can on the floor.
Turn around and walk forward and turn to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Take a step back and look down to face the sink.
Place the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat an apple and place it in the sink.
